verbose_text: Our data demonstrated that the changes in the miR-338 cluster level in physiological conditions resulted in alterations in the expression level of Runx2 and Sox4; meanwhile, Runx2 and Sox4 could greatly influence the expression of both miR-338 and miR-3065 by binding to their promoter regions.
